    },
    {
      "slot": "B",
      "title": "Asking Availability",
      "pattern": "NOUN + 돼요? = Is NOUN available? / Do you VERB?",
      "meaning": "Is NOUN available? / Do you VERB?",
      "explanation": "The verb 돼다 when used with a noun and the question marker -요? is used to ask if something is available or if someone does something. It is a polite way to inquire about the availability of a service or item.",
